Sentencas: We developed a new nickel-free anode for a low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell (LTSOFC) that demonstrated an outstanding electrochemical output of 1000 mW cm(-2) at 550 degrees C.
Titulo: A nanostructure anode (Cu0.2Zn0.8) for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell at 400-600°C

Sentencas: The nanostructure anode had good conductivity and was compatible with cerium oxide-based electrolytes.
Titulo: A nanostructure anode (Cu0.2Zn0.8) for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell at 400-600°C

Sentencas: The performance of a single cell was comparable and or better than those using standard Ni-YSZ and Ni-SDC electrodes (anode).
Titulo: A nanostructure anode (Cu0.2Zn0.8) for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell at 400-600°C

Sentencas: It may have applications for hydrocarbon-based fuel for preventing carbon deposition and replacing nickel in the anode of LTSOFCs.
Titulo: A nanostructure anode (Cu0.2Zn0.8) for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell at 400-600°C
